STATE EX REL. KHAMISI
v.
DETERS. 2017-1707 Supreme Court of Ohio. February 28, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

O'Connor, C.J., and O'Donnell, Kennedy, French, Fischer, DeWine, and DeGenaro, JJ., concur.

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

In Mandamus. On relator's motion for emergency stay of writ of possession pending proceedings. Motion denied. On respondents'motion to dismiss.

Motion granted. Cause dismissed.
